HVAC	O
(	O
which	O
is	O
typically	O
located	O
on	O
a	O
different	O
floor	O
)	O
,	O
in	O
order	O
to	O
initiate	O
equipment	O
operation	O
.	O
This	O
is	O
obviously	O
time	O
consuming	O
and	O
cumbersome	O
.	O

Lastly	O
,	O
there	O
is	O
often	O
an	O
element	O
of	O
